1.  Summary:

    This document outlines the security policy and vulnerability reporting
    procedures for the install-node-version script project.

2.  Contents:

    0.  METADATA ........................................................... 005
    1.  Summary ............................................................ 014
    2.  Contents ........................................................... 020
